Akka OAuthProvider 
------------------

This module is an Akka 2.0 Actor with OAuth 1.0 (only 2-legged) 
support to secure your play based rest-service. 

You can find an example on: 
---------------------------
https://github.com/spirit-fhs/data

See also:
---------
http://code.google.com/p/oauth/
http://akka.io/
https://github.com/typesafehub/play2-mini
http://www.playframework.org/

